    },
    {
      "start": 812.69,
      "end": 818.75,
      "text": "If you start, 만약에 네가 굳이 하고 싶다면, you know, beatboxing, 비트박스라든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 818.75,
      "end": 820.75,
      "text": "Ah, beatboxing. Are you good at beatboxing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 820.97,
      "end": 822.51,
      "text": "Oh, no. How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 822.51,
